<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MediCare+ 병원</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-slate-50">

  {{> common/header-public}}

  <main class="flex-1">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-white overflow-hidden min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-indigo-50/50"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-24">
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
            <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
              <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-indigo-400 opacity-75"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-indigo-500"></span>
            </span>
            스마트 진료 예약 시스템 도입
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">
            당신의 건강한 내일을<br/>
            <span class="text-indigo-600">함께 만들어갑니다</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
            최첨단 의료 장비와 전문 의료진이 환자 중심의 맞춤형 진료를 제공합니다. 빠르고 편리한 스마트 예약 시스템으로 대기 시간을 최소화하세요.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <button
              onclick="location.href='/reservation'"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 group"
            >
              <i data-feather="calendar" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
              진료 예약하기
              <i data-feather="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              onclick="location.href='/reservation/lookup'"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-700 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
            >
              <i data-feather="search" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
              예약 조회
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-lg md:max-w-none relative">
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-indigo-100 to-emerald-50 rounded-3xl transform rotate-3 scale-105"></div>
          <img src="/images/침대.jpg" alt="Hospital Interior" class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl object-cover h-[400px] w-full" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" />

          <!-- Floating Card -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600">
              <i data-feather="check" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">AI 기반</div>
              <div class="text-slate-800 font-bold">맞춤형 증상 분석</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 병원 소개 Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1 relative w-full">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-indigo-100 rounded-3xl transform -rotate-3"></div>
            <img src="/images/병원소개.jpg" alt="병원 전경" class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-xl object-cover h-[400px] md:h-[500px] w-full" referrerPolicy="no-referrer">
            <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 hidden md:block">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-1">20+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">년의 진료 경험</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
              <i data-feather="heart" class="w-4 h-4"></i> About Us
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 leading-tight">
              환자의 마음까지 치유하는<br/>
              <span class="text-indigo-600">따뜻한 병원, 메디케어플러스</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
              메디케어플러스는 2005년 개원 이래, '환자 중심의 의료'라는 철학을 바탕으로 지역 사회의 건강을 책임져 왔습니다. 단순한 질병 치료를 넘어 환자의 마음까지 어루만지는 전인적 치유를 목표로 합니다.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-8">
              <li class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shrink-0">
                  <i data-feather="award" class="w-7 h-7"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">보건복지부 인증 의료기관</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">엄격한 기준을 통과하여 의료 서비스 질과 환자 안전 수준을 공식적으로 인정받았습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shrink-0">
                  <i data-feather="users" class="w-7 h-7"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">분야별 전문의 협진 시스템</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">풍부한 임상 경험을 갖춘 각 분야별 전문 의료진이 협력하여 최적의 치료법을 제시합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-5">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shrink-0">
                  <i data-feather="monitor" class="w-7 h-7"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">대학병원급 최첨단 장비</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">정확한 진단과 안전한 치료를 위해 최신 MRI, CT 등 첨단 의료 장비를 도입하고 있습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 진료 안내 Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">진료 안내</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">체계적이고 전문적인 진료 과목으로 여러분의 건강을 책임집니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8">
          <!-- 내과 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shrink-0">
              <i data-feather="heart" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">내과</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">소화기, 호흡기, 순환기, 내분비 질환 등 성인병 예방 및 만성 질환을 전문적으로 치료합니다.</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-2 font-medium">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-500"></i> 위/대장 내시경 클리닉</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-500"></i> 고혈압, 당뇨 등 만성질환 관리</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 외과 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 shrink-0">
              <i data-feather="scissors" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">외과</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">위장관 질환, 대장항문 질환, 유방/갑상선 질환 등에 대한 전문적인 수술 및 치료를 제공합니다.</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-2 font-medium">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"></i> 최소침습 복강경 수술</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"></i> 화상 및 외상 전문 치료</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 소아청소년과 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 shrink-0">
              <i data-feather="smile" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">소아청소년과</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">신생아부터 청소년까지 성장 단계별 맞춤 진료와 예방 접종, 영유아 검진을 실시합니다.</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-2 font-medium">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-500"></i> 시기별 영유아 건강검진</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-500"></i> 소아 알레르기 및 호흡기 클리닉</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 정형외과 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 shrink-0">
              <i data-feather="activity" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">정형외과</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">척추, 관절 질환 및 스포츠 손상에 대한 비수술적 치료부터 고난도 수술까지 시행합니다.</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-2 font-medium">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500"></i> 인공관절 및 관절내시경 수술</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500"></i> 전문 도수치료 및 재활 센터</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Info Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mb-6">
              <i data-feather="clock" class="w-7 h-7"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">진료 시간</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex justify-between"><span>평일</span> <span class="font-medium">09:00 - 18:00</span></li>
              <li class="flex justify-between"><span>토요일</span> <span class="font-medium">09:00 - 13:00</span></li>
              <li class="flex justify-between text-red-500"><span>일/공휴일</span> <span class="font-medium">휴진</span></li>
              <li class="flex justify-between pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 mt-2"><span>점심시간</span> <span class="font-medium">13:00 - 14:00</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 mb-6">
              <i data-feather="phone" class="w-7 h-7"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">상담 및 문의</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-4">1588-0000</div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              예약 변경 및 취소, 기타 문의사항은<br/>
              고객센터로 연락 주시기 바랍니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  {{> common/footer-public}}

  <script>
    feather.replace();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
